caption: An early Father's Day to an amazing man that God put in our path! Thank you for being an amazing father figure to my princess you are doing a great job and I thank you for it! The word FATHER is a word not everyone deserves and you have earned that title thanks for taking such a big responsibility upon yourself and no matter how hard it was at the beginning you were willing to learn and make it work! We love you with all our hearts HAPPY FATHERS DAY HONEY! #hedidnthavetobe#bradpaisley#lovethissong
